Affected Product
Vendor: WTI (Wireless Technology, Inc.)
Product: WTI Web Management Interface
Component: Camera Control Interface
Version: Camera Control version 3.5.0.r 2024/05/24 00:00:00

Vulnerability Type
Path Traversal / Local File Inclusion (LFI)
CWE: CWE-22 (Improper Limitation of a Pathname to a Restricted Directory)

Impact
An attacker with valid authentication could:
Read sensitive system files
Access configuration data and credentials
Gain information that could facilitate further compromise of the device or connected environment
The vulnerability could lead to information disclosure and increased attack surface for lateral movement.

Mitigation
Apply vendor-provided firmware or software updates if available.
Restrict access to the web management interface using network controls.
Enforce strong authentication and limit administrative access.
Disable the web interface if not required.
Monitor device logs for suspicious file access activity
